iv></div></div></div><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-simpsons-voice-of-milhouse-retires-after-35-years-3814520">米尔豪斯为《辛普森一家》配音 35 年后退休，</a>这一消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
罗德·斯图尔特宣布他已经结束了“大型世界巡演” https://www.nme.com/news/music/rod-stewart-announces-hes-done-with-large-scale-world-tours-3814513?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=rod-stewart-announces-hes-完成大规模世界巡演Max PilleyWed, 20 Nov 2024 20:29:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3814513 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我不想退休，”他澄清道</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rod-stewart-announces-hes-done-with-large-scale-world-tours-3814513">罗德·斯图尔特 (Rod Stewart) 宣布他已结束“大规模世界巡演”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/rod_stewart_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rod-stewart">罗德·斯图尔特 (Rod Stewart)</a>宣布，当他目前的行程结束时，他就结束了“大规模的世界巡演”。</p><p>这位音乐传奇人物已锁定 2025 年的多场演出，包括 2 月/3 月的北美巡演、3 月和 5/6 月的拉斯维加斯驻场巡演、4/5 月的欧洲巡演以及 7/8 月的另一场北美巡演。</p><p>现在，他已经确认这些演出将是他职业生涯中最后的大型舞台演出，并在 Instagram 上写道：“这对我来说将是大规模世界巡演的结束，但我不想退休。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCmryDup2QC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,6