认，随着 1 月份他的 80 岁生日临近，他认为自己的“日子已经屈指可数了”</a> 。 “我知道我的日子屈指可数，但我没有恐惧，”他说。</p><p> “我们都必须在某个时候去世，所以我们都在同一个篮子里。在过去的几年里，我将尽我所能地享受自己。我说很少——可能还有 15 个。我可以轻松做到这一点，伙计，简单。”</p><p>这位摇滚音乐家补充道：“我不像 70 年代和 80 年代那样，我不能熬夜、喝醉、发疯，但仍然有这样的声音。 “现在我必须在每次演出之前和之后保护我的声音。”</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rod-stewart-threatens-to-sell-his-sports-cars-due-to-long-running-battle-over-potholes-3813208">斯图尔特最近威胁要卖掉他的跑车，因为他在埃塞克斯郡哈洛的家附近围绕坑洼展开了长期的斗争</a>。</p><p> 2 月份还有报道称，这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rod-stewart-sells-back-catalogue-for-near-100million-3588728">以接近 1 亿美元（7,930 万英镑）的价格出售了他的过往唱片</a>。斯图尔特与欧文·阿佐夫的标志性艺术家达成了交易，该艺术家现在拥有他的出版目录、录制的音乐以及斯图尔特的肖像权和肖像权的股份。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rod-stewart-announces-hes-done-with-large-scale-world-tours-3814513">罗德·斯图尔特 (Rod Stewart) 宣布他已结束“大规模世界巡演”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 向去世的《巅峰黑帮》服装设计师斯蒂芬妮·科利 (Stephanie Collie) 致敬https://www.nme.com/news/tv/cillian-murphy-leads-tributes-to-peaky-blinders-costume-designer-stephanie-collie-who-has-died-3814498?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=西里安·墨菲领导向《巅峰黑帮》服装设计师斯蒂芬妮·柯利去世致敬Elizabeth AubreyWed, 20 Nov 2024 19:43:29 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3814498 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “斯蒂芬妮是一位才华横溢的人。她发明了‘Peaky Blinders’造型”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/cillian-murphy-leads-tributes-to-peaky-blinders-costume-designer-stephanie-collie-who-has-died-3814498">希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 的帖子向《巅峰黑帮》的服装设计师斯蒂芬妮·科利 (Stephanie Collie) 表示敬意，她去世后</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy)</a>向 60 岁去世的<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/peaky-blinders"><i>《浴血黑帮》</i></a>服装设计师斯蒂芬妮·柯莉 (Stephanie Collie) 致敬。</p><p>许多其他演员也向这位演员致敬，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-reynolds">瑞安·雷诺兹</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-craig">丹尼尔·克雷格</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/samuel-l-jackson">塞缪尔·杰克逊</a>，他们都曾与这位著名的服装设计师合作过。</p><p>这一消息通过英国广播公司<i>《浴血黑帮</i>》官方 Instagram 账户与粉丝们分享，并向 Collie 的“鼓舞人心”的工作表示敬意。</p><p>声明中写道：“得知服装设计师斯蒂芬妮·科利去世的消息，我们感到非常悲伤。</p><p> “斯蒂芬妮在我们的第一个系列中所做的令人难以置信的工作是创造<i>《浴血黑帮》</i>标志性外观的关键，并继续激励着世界各地的许多人。</p><p> “我们的爱和思念与她的家人同在。”</p><p>墨菲在剧中扮演汤米·谢尔比<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tommy-shelby-returns-in-peaky-blinders-movie-first-look-image-3798419#:~:text=Production%20has%20begun%20on%20Netflix,Cillian%20Murphy%20as%20Tommy%20Shelby.&amp;text=The%20film%20was%20first%20confirmed,Tom%20Harper%20set%20to%20direct.">，目前正在拍摄新的衍生电影</a>，他分享了他对柯利犬的深情致敬。</p><p>他在一份声明中写道：“斯蒂芬妮是一位才华横溢的人。她发明的<i>《浴血黑帮》的</i>外观和轮廓已成为全世界的标志。</p><p> “我们都会想念她的。安息吧。” </p><blockquote class="instagra