buy-tickets-3497458">与奥利维亚·罗德里戈一起参加了她的“Guts”世界巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kim-deal-shares-warm-new-single-nobody-loves-you-more-announces-2025-us-and-uk-tour-dates-tickets-3814499">Kim Deal 分享温暖的新单曲“Nobody Loves You More”并宣布 2025 年美国和英国巡演日期的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
艾尔顿·约翰和杰克·希尔斯的音乐剧《Tammy Faye》在上映几周后就结束了https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-and-jake-shears-tammy-faye-musical-to-close-just-weeks-after-opening-3814491?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=埃尔顿·约翰和杰克·剪子塔米·费耶音乐剧将在上映几周后关闭Max PilleyWed, 20 Nov 2024 18:40:34 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3814491 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>到关闭时，百老汇演出将只剩下 29 场常规演出</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-and-jake-shears-tammy-faye-musical-to-close-just-weeks-after-opening-3814491">艾尔顿·约翰 (Elton John) 和杰克·希尔斯 (Jake Shears) 合作的音乐剧《塔米·费伊》(Tammy Faye) 在开演几周后就</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上首播。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/elton_jake_shears-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont